column5: Hey Guys,   Heading up to the cottage next week and was just wondering how the ice is holding up to all this warm weather.  Any information would be appreciated!!  Thanks
I was fishing in the area today and it is good to go, a bit slushy in spots but there are snow machines on the lakes
right on......hopefully it is good this coming thursday!!!
Ice is fine, didn't really get much warmer than +2 or +3 around there all last week.
